```
SELECT 
  name, 
  contact_no, 
  nid, 
  COUNT(*) AS num_missing 
FROM 
  customer_dim 
WHERE 
  name IS NULL 
GROUP BY 
  name, 
  contact_no, 
  nid 
ORDER BY 
  num_missing DESC;
```
